snippet.title: F💔💔k You Witch - Release Trailer. (Official Video).
snippet.description:
The Game on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2736020/Fuck_You_Witch/

The Soundtrack on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2822410/Fuck_You_Witch_Soundtrack/

Your best friend has confessed her love for you... but the problems don't stop there. You've started to hallucinate. All this interferes with sleeping and eating, and in general disrupts your ideal lifestyle.

Prepare beshbarmak, yell obseneties at the witch, immerse yourself in the atmosphere of the Kazakh steppes, and try figuring out what the fuck is going on.

Use a microphone because only Russian obscenities can save you from a witch.

If your Mom is home and there is no way to yell obscenities at the witch, then you can disable this function.

But make sure to wear headphones, because the main character will swear at your behalf, and the chance of getting a bollocking from your parents is very high.
